text: These species of tree frogs in the Hylidae family are commonly referred to as the Arizona tree frog: *Canyon tree frog, Hyla arenicolor *Mountain tree frog, Hyla eximia is listed as the official Arizona state amphibian, but it does not occur in Arizona. *Arizona tree frog, Hyla wrightorum, was previously a synonym of Hyla eximia.
title: Arizona tree frog
